Localization.Name: Doomsday
Localization.Description: Extremely aggressive looking homemade armor meant to protect and intimidate. This kind of armor is not only expected to survive the apocalypse, but also dominate its aftermath.

English.Name: Doomsday
English.Description: Extremely aggressive looking homemade armor meant to protect and intimidate. This kind of armor is not only expected to survive the apocalypse, but also dominate its aftermath.

Localization.Name: - Survivalist Heavy Helmet White-Blue
Localization.Description:
Item Type: Heavy Armor
Damage Reduction: 40%
Temp. Rating: -77 / 107 °C
Radiation Protection: 26800 REM
Radiation Scrub Rate: 145.8 REM/s

Remain fully protected and anonymous without feeling a great weight on your head. The Overlord helmet delivers heavy armor protection while using a special lightweight composite plating that makes it feel like nothing's there. Repurposed ocular sensors normally found on ships keep you attuned to your surroundings and, when worn with the full Overlord suit, the high neck collar provides the helmet extra support and protection. Visor is AR crosshair compatible.
